text: Ösökhbayaryn Chagnaadorj (born ) is a Mongolian male weightlifter, competing in the 56 kg category and representing Mongolia at international competitions. He participated at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 56 kg event. After his performance he had an IOC out-of-competition test and tested positive on exogenous testosterone.CAS: CAS OG AD 16/08 International Olympic Committee v.
